{"type":"finding","iteration":13,"id":"S2-05B-mergeable-selection-gate","dimension":"D1","focus":"S2-05","summary":"Kasper suppresses re-proposal by loading rejected_patterns into ctx.rejectedPatterns and checking pending or auto-improvement weaknesses against every rejected pattern with weaknessesMergeable before surfacing or applying them.","sourceRefs":[".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/index.ts:362",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/types.ts:405",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/types.ts:407",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/evaluate.ts:1659",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/evaluate.ts:1660",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/evaluate.ts:1661",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/evaluate.ts:1662",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/evaluate.ts:1673",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/handlers.ts:419",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/handlers.ts:422",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/handlers.ts:423",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:237",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:243",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:250",".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/156-agent-loops-improved/external/kasper/src/utils.ts:252"],"targetFile":".opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/